<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_04b73d65-feb6-45aa-9a93-09347172a3ec" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>E1D9</sptc><title id="_72ffdced-5f3c-4637-b95b-afc5e37b17cb">Where sprinklers are required: Class 7a building</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_b1b00284-98db-4a90-a499-dc7a38bfe929" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_192d0c3b-5b32-44d7-b266-53c4978a6bfa">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In a Class 7a building, other than an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1384_4.0.0.xml#_98f99be0-5c03-48a8-8087-27bc99acc90d" id="_560d6a1a-2bdb-458b-9cf9-8652a5fca40c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">open-deck carpark</xref> which is a separate building, sprinklers are <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_33728d25-cd16-4e93-be05-82782aeb2435" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1277_2.0.0.xml#_524b0326-5823-4ddc-9eb3-adab587568e8" id="_29de274f-1f17-4088-864b-dd6180978ba8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire compartments</xref> where—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_7c03c68b-0745-42cd-bac4-ebd217126999">more than 40 vehicles are accommodated; or</li><li id="_1579c087-8bd3-4e75-8c86-8b0f7c2087ce">a carstacker is installed.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_fe94c9df-2072-4800-ac04-00f287f8f3c1"><callout-type ncc-info-type="notes"/><p>A carstacker is a machine that stores 2 or more cars in a vertical arrangement such that one or more cars may not be accessible from floor level.</p></callout></clause>